    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以StockLevel是入口状态，Creating是中间转换节点。这两个通道Writer和Reader需要做成复合状态吗？另外，Creating还要连到FleetManagement吗？",
