      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Writer和Reader都做成复合状态。FleetManagement也要从Creating引过去，表示创建操作会同步通知车队管理系统。Writer内部从Warehouse进入Writing状态，Reader内部从TrackingNumber进入Reading状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Writer",
        "Reader",
