      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主框架画出来：StockLevel指向Creating，Creating分出三条线——到Writer、到Reader、到FleetManagement。两个复合状态也建好了，Warehouse-Writing在Writer里，TrackingNumber-Reading在Reader里。",
      "elements_involved": [
