      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来补全异常和关闭流程。Writer这边，Writing结束后要Disconnecting，然后ClosingReader，最后回到Creating可以复用。Reader这边，Reading可能遇到Error，然后ClosingWriter，同样回到Creating。",
